Duration: 30-60 seconds
Style: Fast-paced, visually dynamic
Music: Upbeat, tech-inspired background track

[Opening Shot]
Text overlay: "In 1879, Edison lit up the world..."
*Show vintage footage/images of first electric lights*

[Transition]
Text: "In 2025, AI is powering our future..."
*Quick montage of modern AI applications*

Key Segments:

1. "Just like electricity transformed every industry..."
- Show split-screen: Old factory vs. AI-powered automation
- Healthcare: Traditional X-ray vs. AI diagnosis
- Transportation: Horse carriage vs. self-driving cars

2. "AI is becoming as essential as turning on a light"
*Show everyday AI applications*
- Smart home devices
- Virtual assistants
- Personalized recommendations

3. Engaging Statistics (animated)
- "90% of leading businesses use AI"
- "AI market growing 38% annually"
- "By 2030, AI will add $15.7 trillion to global economy"

